      "description": "THE DRIVING QUESTION: For each community area, monthly crime count vs avg Divvy bikes available. Since Divvy station reads lack community_area_id (GBFS doesn't include it), this is a proxy — total bikes available system-wide per month, alongside monthly crime counts. A real join requires geospatial matching (Phase 4+).",
